 2. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 3. the person who's sport is baseball is on the far left##1
 4. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 5. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
 6. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
 7. the owner of the hamster is on the far right##1
 8. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
 9. the person who's hobby is dancing is the person who's sport is cricket##1
10. the person who's hobby is fishing is in the middle##1
11. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
12. the owner of the snake is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
13. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
14. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3    |       4       |    5     |
| Beverage      | 7up        | iced-tea   | coffee  | fanta         | lemonade |
