The people use 5 different means of transport: airplane, bike, quad-bike, scooter, skateboard
 1. the fan of soul is the person playing chess##1
 2. the person playing canasta is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 3. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the fan of country##1
 4. the person playing snooker is the person driving the airplane##1
 5. the fan of r&b is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
 6. the person driving the airplane is the fan of electronic##1
 7. the person drinking water is the fan of electronic##1
 8. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
 9. the person playing snooker is on the far left##1
10. the person driving the quad-bike is the person drinking juice##1
11. the person playing billiard is the fan of folk##1
12. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
13. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
14. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |     3      |      4       |     5      |
