 5. the fonseca-smoker is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
 6. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 7. the alhambra-smoker is the owner of the ferret##1
 8. the fan of blues is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1
 9. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
10. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
11. the owner of the pony is on the left of the cain-smoker##1
12. the baccarat-smoker is the fan of house##1
13. the cain-smoker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |      3       |   4    |    5     |
| Beverage      | 7up      | cola       | milk         | juice  | iced-tea |
| Cigar   | baccarat  | game | alhambra | fonseca  | cain  |
| Music-Genre   | house    | country    | blues        | reggae | folk     |
| Pet           | hedgehog | mouse      | ferret       | pony   | rabbit   |

